<h2>Sore tongue, Thick saliva or mucus and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms sore tongue, thick saliva or mucus and white patches on tongue including Allergic reaction, Dehydration (Children), and Thrush (infants and children).</p>
<p>There  are 9 conditions  associated with sore tongue, thick saliva or mucus and white patches on tongue. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
</div>
